Buying a Cars24 Certified Used Car Online in Australia- Step by Step

  1. Browse our wide inventory

    Explore a wide range of selection of Toyota, BMW, Audi, Mercedes-Benz, Honda, Hyundai and many more. Each car we offer comes with extensive inspection and PPSR reports for well-informed decision. 

  2. Start the process online or book a test drive

    Our process is 100% online but if you test the car you wish to drive, you can book a test drive with us. You will have to book a slot and fill in relevant information for test drive and if you don’t want to test, you can simply choose to make purchase online.

  3. Get finance (if needed)

    If you require a loan, Cars24 offers pre-approved loans as well. Our process is quick and can be easily done alongside car selection.

  4. Make payment and complete purchase

    Finalise your purchase by selecting the car and making the payment through your preferred method. You can choose to pay online or opt for financing. 

  5. Enjoy your Car

    Once the purchase is complete, you can drive your pre-owned car backed by our support.

Car History Check

Extended Warranty

Finance Pre-Approved
